程序包 xyz.fsgik.annotations

  • 注释类型概要 
    注释类型 说明
    AcceptedType
    Declares type of the annotated element is allowed to be the specified type.
    AcceptedTypes
    Declares type of the annotated element is allowed to be the specified types.
    DefaultNonNull
    Declares the annotated element and all methods, fields parameters, local variables and type uses in its scope must not be null.
    DefaultNullable
    Declares the annotated element and all methods, fields parameters, local variables and type uses in its scope may be null.
    Immutable
    Declares the annotated element is immutable.
    NonNull
    Declares the annotated element must not be null.
    Nullable
    Declares the annotated element may be null.
    OutParam
    Declares the annotated element is an output parameter that can be modified.
    RejectedType
    Declares type of the annotated element is not allowed to be the specified type.
    RejectedTypes
    Declares type of the annotated element is not allowed to be the specified types.
    ThreadSafe
    Declares the annotated element is thread-safe in its scope.
